---
layout: layouts/inner.njk
title: Sustainability
permalink: /sustainability/
eyebrow:
  en: Sustainability
  vi: Phát triển bền vững
  zh: 可持续发展
heading:
  en: Growing Together. Responsibly.
  vi: Cùng nhau phát triển. Có trách nhiệm.
  zh: 共同成长。负责任地前行。
lead:
  en: Sustainability is how Nam Viet operates — responsible sourcing, people-first partnerships, and transparent governance.
  vi: Phát triển bền vững là cách Nam Việt vận hành — nguyên liệu có trách nhiệm, đồng hành con người, quản trị minh bạch.
  zh: 可持续发展是南越的运营方式——负责任采购、以人为本的合作与透明治理。
---

<nav class="page-subnav" aria-label="Sustainability sections" data-page-subnav>
  <div class="page-subnav__inner">
    <a href="#overview" class="page-subnav__link is-active" data-subnav-target="overview">
      <span class="lang en">Overview</span>
      <span class="lang vi">Tổng quan</span>
      <span class="lang zh">概览</span>
    </a>
    {% for pillar in sustainability.pillars %}
    <a
      href="#{{ pillar.id }}"
      class="page-subnav__link"
      data-subnav-target="{{ pillar.id }}"
    >
      <span class="esg-nav__letter" aria-hidden="true">{{ pillar.letter }}</span>
      <span class="lang en">{{ pillar.title.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ pillar.title.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ pillar.title.zh }}</span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
    <a href="#standards" class="page-subnav__link" data-subnav-target="standards">
      <span class="lang en">Standards</span>
      <span class="lang vi">Chuẩn mực</span>
      <span class="lang zh">标准</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="esg-page">
  <section id="overview" class="esg-page__intro page-panel" data-page-panel="overview">
    <div class="esg-page__banner">
      <img
        src="{{ '/assets/img/sustainability.png' | url }}"
        alt="Sustainable agriculture and responsible operations at Nam Viet Group"
        loading="lazy"
        width="1400"
        height="700"
      >
      <div class="esg-page__banner-veil" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="esg-page__banner-label">
        <span class="lang en">ESG framework</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Khung ESG</span>
        <span class="lang zh">ESG 框架</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="esg-page__approach">
      <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.approach.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.approach.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.approach.zh }}</span>
    </p>

    <ul class="esg-page__principles" aria-label="ESG principles">
      {% for item in sustainability.principles %}
      <li>
        <span class="lang en">{{ item.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ item.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ item.zh }}</span>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <div class="esg-highlights" aria-label="ESG highlights">
      {% for item in sustainability.highlights %}
      <div class="esg-highlight{% if item.wide %} esg-highlight--wide{% endif %}">
        <p class="esg-highlight__value">{{ item.value }}</p>
        <p class="esg-highlight__label">
          <span class="lang en">{{ item.label.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ item.label.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ item.label.zh }}</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="esg-chain" aria-labelledby="esg-chain-title">
    <header class="esg-section__head">
      <h2 id="esg-chain-title">
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.chain.title.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.chain.title.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.chain.title.zh }}</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.chain.lead.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.chain.lead.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.chain.lead.zh }}</span>
      </p>
    </header>
    <ol class="esg-chain__steps">
      {% for step in sustainability.chain.steps %}
      <li class="esg-chain__step">
        <span class="esg-chain__num" aria-hidden="true">{{ step.num }}</span>
        <h3>
          <span class="lang en">{{ step.title.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ step.title.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ step.title.zh }}</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          <span class="lang en">{{ step.text.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ step.text.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ step.text.zh }}</span>
        </p>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <div class="esg-page__pillars">
    {% for pillar in sustainability.pillars %}
    <article
      id="{{ pillar.id }}"
      class="esg-block page-panel"
      data-page-panel="{{ pillar.id }}"
    >
      <div class="esg-block__main">
        <header class="esg-block__head">
          <span class="esg-block__letter" aria-hidden="true">{{ pillar.letter }}</span>
          <div class="esg-block__titles">
            <p class="esg-block__eyebrow">
              <span class="lang en">Pillar {{ loop.index }}</span>
              <span class="lang vi">Trụ cột {{ loop.index }}</span>
              <span class="lang zh">支柱 {{ loop.index }}</span>
            </p>
            <h2 class="esg-block__title">
              <span class="lang en">{{ pillar.title.en }}</span>
              <span class="lang vi">{{ pillar.title.vi }}</span>
              <span class="lang zh">{{ pillar.title.zh }}</span>
            </h2>
          </div>
        </header>
        <p class="esg-block__lead">
          <span class="lang en">{{ pillar.lead.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ pillar.lead.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ pillar.lead.zh }}</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="esg-block__list">
        {% for focus in pillar.focuses %}
        <li>
          <span class="esg-block__mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lang en">{{ focus.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ focus.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ focus.zh }}</span>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <section id="standards" class="esg-standards page-panel" data-page-panel="standards">
    <header class="esg-section__head">
      <h2>
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.standards.title.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.standards.title.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.standards.title.zh }}</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.standards.lead.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.standards.lead.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.standards.lead.zh }}</span>
      </p>
    </header>
    <div class="esg-standards__grid">
      {% for item in sustainability.standards.items %}
      <article class="esg-standard">
        <p class="esg-standard__code">{{ item.code }}</p>
        <h3>
          <span class="lang en">{{ item.title.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ item.title.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ item.title.zh }}</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          <span class="lang en">{{ item.text.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ item.text.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ item.text.zh }}</span>
        </p>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <aside class="esg-story">
    <div class="esg-story__media">
      <img
        src="{{ '/assets/img/sustainability.png' | url }}"
        alt=""
        loading="lazy"
        width="800"
        height="560"
      >
    </div>
    <div class="esg-story__body">
      <p class="esg-story__eyebrow">
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.story.eyebrow.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.story.eyebrow.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.story.eyebrow.zh }}</span>
      </p>
      <h2>
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.story.title.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.story.title.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.story.title.zh }}</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.story.text.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.story.text.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.story.text.zh }}</span>
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn--solid" href="{{ sustainability.story.href | url }}">
        <span class="lang en">{{ sustainability.story.cta.en }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ sustainability.story.cta.vi }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ sustainability.story.cta.zh }}</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <aside class="esg-page__cta">
    <div class="esg-page__cta-copy">
      <h2>
        <span class="lang en">Go deeper</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Tìm hiểu thêm</span>
        <span class="lang zh">深入了解</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <span class="lang en">Download ESG highlights or talk with our team about responsible partnership.</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Tải điểm nhấn ESG hoặc trao đổi với chúng tôi về hợp tác có trách nhiệm.</span>
        <span class="lang zh">下载 ESG 要点，或与我们讨论负责任的合作。</span>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="esg-page__cta-actions">
      <a class="btn btn--solid" href="{{ '/downloads/' | url }}">
        <span class="lang en">Download ESG highlights</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Tải điểm nhấn ESG</span>
        <span class="lang zh">下载 ESG 要点</span>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn--outline btn--dark" href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}">
        <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.contact }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.contact }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.contact }}</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
